{"id":1567,"date":"2021-03-03T13:09:31","date_gmt":"2021-03-03T13:09:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/mapus.io\/?p=1567"},"modified":"2023-06-22T11:41:14","modified_gmt":"2023-06-22T11:41:14","slug":"roadmap-digital-transformation","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/getting-started-digital-transformation\/roadmap-digital-transformation\/","title":{"rendered":"The MapUs roadmap to digital transformation"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"1567\" class=\"elementor elementor-1567\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-19202a21 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"19202a21\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;shape_divider_bottom&quot;:&quot;opacity-fan&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shape elementor-shape-bottom\" data-negative=\"false\">\n\t\t\t<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 283.5 19.6\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" style=\"opacity:0.33\" d=\"M0 0L0 18.8 141.8 4.1 283.5 18.8 283.5 0z\"\/>\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" style=\"opacity:0.33\" d=\"M0 0L0 12.6 141.8 4 283.5 12.6 283.5 0z\"\/>\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" style=\"opacity:0.33\" d=\"M0 0L0 6.4 141.8 4 283.5 6.4 283.5 0z\"\/>\n\t<path class=\"elementor-shape-fill\" d=\"M0 0L0 1.2 141.8 4 283.5 1.2 283.5 0z\"\/>\n<\/svg>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-53ac70fc\" data-id=\"53ac70fc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-3d58277d elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3d58277d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-28d45b97\" data-id=\"28d45b97\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-300f43dd eael-dual-header-content-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"300f43dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">The MapUs roadmap to<\/span> <span>successful Digital transformation <\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p>We often get asked how you create a roadmap to digital transformation. With MapUs, the roadmap is pretty much laid out in front of you &#8211; you just have to know how to read it. In this guide, we&#8217;ll walk you through how to achieve and sustain digital transformation using MapUs in 5 steps.\u00a0<\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5a712577 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5a712577\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5b3f58b4\" data-id=\"5b3f58b4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-66d43fa0 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"66d43fa0\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-470e0545\" data-id=\"470e0545\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-52ebee30 eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"52ebee30\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Introduction: <\/span> <span>The Digital transformation cycle<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There\u2019s no set definition of what a digital transformation is, but our many years of experience in the field has led us to an understanding of digital transformation as a <strong>cyclical process<\/strong>. One where you constantly grow and learn and never stop being curious about what digital potential remains untapped. <\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In other words, before you even begin the process, think of digital transformation as a continuous project, where the goal isn&#8217;t just about strengthening your digital capacity in one go, but about fostering, anchoring and sustaining a digital mindset<\/span><\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-1ac112f3\" data-id=\"1ac112f3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f51becb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f51becb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"631\" src=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/Skaermbillede-2021-03-18-kl.-19.38.23.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2627\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/Skaermbillede-2021-03-18-kl.-19.38.23.png 864w, https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/Skaermbillede-2021-03-18-kl.-19.38.23-600x474.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-57fc55d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"57fc55d\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-62124a4\" data-id=\"62124a4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9946f4c elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"9946f4c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-735ff353 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"735ff353\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2fa6388b\" data-id=\"2fa6388b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-1ba52fa8 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1ba52fa8\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-4576fd4\" data-id=\"4576fd4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-350ba46 eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"350ba46\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Step 1: <\/span> <span>Define your purpose <\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the things that excite our users the most about MapUs, is that it makes digitization and digital transformation feel accessible and empowering. They\u2019re often eager to start right away. <strong>But if you don\u2019t have a clear goal to steer you, the process can easily become more overwhelming than exciting<\/strong>. That is why the first step of any digital transformation is defining your purpose, beyond just wanting to strengthen your general digital capacity. Be specific about the outcomes you want to achieve, e.g.:\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f6ab8eb elementor-icon-list--layout-traditional elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"f6ab8eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">A comprehensive, collective overview of the organizations digital strengths and weaknesses<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">A vocabulary to talk about what it means to be digitally competent in your specific organization<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">A data based foundation for evaluation and creating a digital strategy<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d64fc50 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"d64fc50\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31096bc eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"31096bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Step 2:  <\/span> <span>Kickstart the digital dialogue with MapUs<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you\u2019ve defined your purpose, it\u2019s time to begin working actively with digital competence by having your organization complete the MapUs self-assessment. Because our assessment is based on self-reflection and creates a shared experience, it naturally lends itself to kickstarting the digital dialogue in your organization.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your organization will suddenly have a shared language, with which to talk about digitalization and we strongly recommend that you encourage that conversation. <strong>In our experience, the most successful transformations happen when you let your employees use their new vocabulary to talk about how digitalization impacts their lives, both professionally and<\/strong> <strong>personally<\/strong>. Workshops and webinars where the employees get to reflect on their digital strengths and weaknesses can thus be a great way to support the growth happening in step 2.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\u2019s important to keep stimulating and encouraging the digital dialogue, if you want to ingrain a digital mindset in your organization and in the individual employee. Two concrete examples of ways to do this could be:\u00a0<\/span><\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d2d933 elementor-icon-list--layout-traditional elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"6d2d933\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Have it on the agenda for your next performance reviews<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Create individual digital development plans for all your employees<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-30772d2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"30772d2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0209aea eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"0209aea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Step 3:<\/span> <span>Let the data guide your strategy<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After spending some time fostering digital dialogue and instilling a digital mindset in your employees, you should redirect your focus to the big picture and the actual data generated from the assessment. Step 3 will often be carried out in the context of Management, HR or Digitalization and is all about figuring out how the MapUs data can inform and support your digital strategy.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The great thing about MapUs at this step, is that our powerful data motor does all the work of gathering, analyzing and visualizing the data for you, in a way that makes it easy to identify strengths and weaknesses. <strong>All you have to do is interpret the analyses and select the results that you find most meaningful to work with going forward.<\/strong> It\u2019s important to emphasize that once the data has been collected, the only limitation to how you can use it is your imagination. Below, we\u2019ve gathered some of the most common ways to let the data help you unlock your organization\u2019s digital potential: <\/span><\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a9b5aba elementor-icon-list--layout-traditional elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"a9b5aba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Identify employees who needs a competence boost in selected areas of importance<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Identify digital frontrunners who can be ambassadors in driving the digital development in your organization<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Put digitalization on the agenda in team meetings by presenting specified reports<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Identify your greatest potentials for and threats to digitalization across teams, departments and management levels<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">List Create plans of action for teams, departments or management levels to improve their digital capacity<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-circle-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">Create \u201cpersonas\u201d in MapUs for specific digital competence profiles and skills sets, you want to work with <\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90e0e05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"90e0e05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee3f770 eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"ee3f770\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Step 4: <\/span> <span>Fostering growth<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you reach Step 4, it\u2019s time to put your strategy into action and begin educating your employees and helping them grow their digital capabilities. There are numerous ways to do this such as employing an LMS system, creating courses and seminars or perhaps tutorials. <strong>When working with MapUs, the resource module is a great element to utilize strategically in this phase.<\/strong> It lets you create a direct link between the digital competences and the specific resource an employee needs to seek out, encouraging them to take action.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Resources can be categorized didactically, taxonomically or perhaps like we\u2019ve done it in the MapUs resource catalogue &#8211; examples (why is this competence relevant to me), benefits (what do I get out of being good at it) and exercises (how do I improve).\u00a0 Either way you choose to do it, the point is that the employee should be met with resources that make sense, that motivates them to learn and that gives them specific instructions on how to begin improving. <\/span><\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b851be4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"b851be4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e0d5dd eael-dual-header-content-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"0e0d5dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-dual-header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"title\"><span class=\"lead solid-color\">Step 5: <\/span> <span>Completing and restarting the cycle<\/span><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"subtext\"><p>This final step is about regrouping and looking ahead. When you\u2019ve wrapped up your initial efforts to strengthen the digital competence level in your organization, you need to assess whether they\u2019ve been fruitful or if you need to rethink your strategy. <strong>MapUs provides a great starting point for this evaluation with the benchmarking tool, which allows you to gather data on your organization&#8217;s progress from the outset up to now.<\/strong> And just like that, the cycle has been completed and restarted.<\/p><p>The information you gather in this step will be the <strong>knowledge<\/strong> you use to finetune your <strong>strategy<\/strong>, which encompasses a new set of efforts to <strong>educate<\/strong> your organization and continue to get smarter together. This continued growth happens when you keep documenting the development across your organization, and it can take on many different forms. You might be inspired to do a yearly check in your digital progress, or perhaps the insights gathered in step 3 will inspire you to recruit new people. Either way, a digital transformation with MapUs will keep you curious and empowered to unlock the full potential of your organization.<\/p><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10b6f15 content-align-cta-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-cta-box\" data-id=\"10b6f15\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-cta-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-call-to-action cta-basic bg-lite cta-preset-1\">\n        <h2 class=\"title\">Want to hear how others have succeeded using MapUs?<\/h2><p>Book a free session with one of our experts to learn more about the MapUs solutions.<\/p><a href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/contact-and-support\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"cta-button  \">Book a session<\/a>\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-335c179 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"335c179\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d0ed768\" data-id=\"d0ed768\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11c631e elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"11c631e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-250bc3c eael-dual-header-content-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-dual-color-header\" data-id=\"250bc3c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"eael-dual-color-header.default\">\n\t\t\t