ng you to create the competence model that&#8217;s a perfect fit for you<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/survey-building\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about Survey building\" tabindex=\"-1\" >\n\t\t\tRead More \u00bb\t\t<\/a>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__meta-data\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-date\">\n\t\t\t2021-03-11\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-avatar\">\n\t\t\tNo Comments\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-2030 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__card\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__text\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-post__title\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/getting-started-digital-transformation\/internal-facilitation\/\" >\n\t\t\t\tInternal facilitation\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__excerpt\">\n\t\t\t<p>Want to know how to use MapUs in workshop situations? Or do you want to explore the possibilities of date driven performance reviews? The check out our guides on how you can use MapUs for internal facilitation. <\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/getting-started-digital-transformation\/internal-facilitation\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about Internal facilitation\" tabindex=\"-1\" >\n\t\t\tRead More \u00bb\t\t<\/a>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__meta-data\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-date\">\n\t\t\t2021-03-09\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-avatar\">\n\t\t\tNo Comments\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-1959 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__card\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__text\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-post__title\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/getting-started-digital-transformation\/preparation-guide\/\" >\n\t\t\t\tMapUs preparation guide\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__excerpt\">\n\t\t\t<p>Good preparation is underrated. To make sure you get the best possible start to your digital journey, we\u2019ve gathered some important points of reflection. <\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/mapus.io\/knowledge-base\/getting-started-digital-transformation\/preparation-guide\/\" aria-label=\"Read more about MapUs preparation guide\" tabindex=\"-1\" >\n\t\t\tRead More \u00bb\t\t<\/a>\n\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__meta-data\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-date\">\n\t\t\t2021-03-09\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-post-avatar\">\n\t\t\tNo Comments\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/article>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We often get asked how you create a roadmap to digital transformation. With MapUs, the roadmap is pretty much laid out in front of you &#8211; you just have to know how to read it.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":0,"parent":1327,"menu_order":3,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_eb_attr":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1567","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1567","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/mapus.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":t